<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title>Money Mind</title>
    <style>
        *{
            font-family:'Lucida Sans', 'Lucida Sans Regular', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        header{
                
                 background-color: black;
                 
        } 
        .header{
                    margin-top: 10px;
                    background-color: white;
                    display:flex;
                    height:60px;
                    justify-content: space-between;
                align-items: center;
                
                
                   
             }
             .navbar {

    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    text-decoration: none;
}

.navbar ul{
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    text-decoration: none;
   
}

.navbar ul li a{
    margin: 0 20px;
    color:black;

    text-decoration: none;
}
        .navbar ul li a:hover {
            text-shadow: #000000;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .menu-toggle {
    display: none;
    background-color: #000000;
    border: none;
    color: white;
    padding: 10px;
    font-size: 16px;

}

        .hero-section {
           
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 80vh;
            color:black;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .hero-section h2 {
            font-size: 3em;
            /* color: #ffcb05; */
            color:black;
        }
        .hero-section p {
            color:black;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .cta-btn {
            background-color: #ff6347;
            border: none;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .cta-btn:hover {
            background-color: #ff4500;
        }
        .features {
            padding: 50px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .features h3 {
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .feature-cards {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .feature-card {
            background-color: #ebe4e4;
            color:black;
            width: 30%;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border:solid;
            border-width:1px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .feature-card h4 {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: black;
        }


        .footer {
            background-color: #ebe4e4;
            color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #000000;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            color: #000000;
        }
        /* Media Queries for responsiveness */
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .menu-toggle {
        display: block; /* Show menu button on mobile */
    }
    .navbar ul {
        display: none; /* Initially hidden */
        flex-direction: column;
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        right: 0; /* Align to the right */
        height: 80px; /* Full height */
        width: 150px; /* Adjust width as needed */
         /* Offset for header */
        transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
        transform: translateX(100%); /* Hidden off-screen to the right */
    }
    .navbar li{
        margin-top: 5px;
         text-shadow: 0px 0px 20px #000000;
    
    }

    .navbar.active ul {
        margin-top: 70px;
        display: flex;
        transform: translateX(0); /* Slide-in effect */
    }
     .logo img{
        width:200px;
    }
    .hero-section h2{
       font-size: 35px;
    }

    
}


    </style>
</head>
<body id="home">

    <header>
      <div class="header">
         <div class="logo" style="margin-top: 60px;">
           <img src="html/moneymind2.png" alt="Money Mind Logo" width="350px">
         </div>
         <div class="navbar">
            <button class="menu-toggle">Menu</button>
            <ul class="menu">
                <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a></li>
                <li><a href="#about-us">About Us</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact-us">Contact Us</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
      </div>
    </header>
    <hr>

    <section class="hero-section">
        <div>
            <h2>Track Your Spending Effortlessly</h2>
            <p>Monitor, analyze, and take control of your finances with ease.</p>
            <button class="cta-btn" onclick="window.location.href='/signin'">Start Tracking</button>
        </div>
    </section>


    <section class="features">
        <h3>Why Use Expense Tracker?</h3>
        <div class="feature-cards">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <h4>Real-time Monitoring</h4>
                <p>Track your daily, weekly, and monthly expenses with live updates.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <h4>Custom Categories</h4>
                <p>Personalize your expense categories to match your lifestyle.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <h4>Visual Reports</h4>
                <p>Generate beautiful charts and reports to analyze your spending patterns.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <hr>

    <section id="privacy-policy" class="footer">
        <h3>Privacy Policy</h3>
        <p>Your data is safe with us. We respect your privacy and do not share your information with third parties.</p>
    </section>
    <hr>

    <section id="about-us" class="footer">
        <h3>About Us</h3>
        <p>Expense Tracker is dedicated to helping you manage your finances with ease. Our mission is to make budgeting stress-free.</p>
    </section>
<hr>
    <section id="contact-us" class="footer">
        <h3>Contact Us</h3>
        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to <a href="mailto:support@expensetracker.com">contact us</a>.</p>
    </section>
<hr>
    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Expense Tracker. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
<script>
    document.querySelector('.menu-toggle').addEventListener('click', function() {
    document.querySelector('.navbar').classList.toggle('active');
});
</script>
</body>
</html>